structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
PUBLIC WORKS IN CITIES OTHER THAN THE FIRST CLASS

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 165, sec. 34. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2741e-7, 2741e-9.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Tax for cost may be paid half when work begun, remainder when half completed; assessment of property owned by governmental agency.
